@startuml
[*] --> Start
Start --> Restart : Restart
Restart --> ConfigMode : Configuration Mode Required
ConfigMode --> Running : Configuration Completed
Running --> CollectData : Clock Triggered
CollectData --> Running : Data Collection Complete
Running --> PrepareSummary : Summary Request Received
PrepareSummary --> Running : Summary Prepared
Running --> CheckStatus : Status Request Received
CheckStatus --> Running : Status Checked
Running --> ControlledMode : Remote Control Command Received
ControlledMode --> ShutDown : Shutdown Command Received
ShutDown --> [*] : Shutdown Complete

@enduml
